        ]
      },
      "date": "2012-12-23 17:00:12.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: Verified\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.3/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/bc52ed2c-4d1e-11e2-bf7d-52540035b04c).  Ran 12 tests.  No failures.",
