      "date": "2013-01-08 23:24:00.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nIt's much better now (no crashes).  But I can still trigger infinite cats (read() does not return 0):\n\n llmount.sh\ncat /proc/fs/lustre/mds/MDS/mdt_seqm/req_history\necho 'Nijn is jarig!' > /mnt/lustre/motd\ncat /proc/fs/lustre/mds/MDS/mdt_seqm/req_history\n-1:0@lo:12345-0@lo:x1423637870543084:264:Complete:1357686943:0s(-11s) opc 700\n-1:0@lo:12345-0@lo:x1423637870543084:264:Complete:1357686943:0s(-11s) opc 700\n-1:0@lo:12345-0@lo:x1423637870543084:264:Complete:1357686943:0s(-11s) opc 700\n-1:0@lo:12345-0@lo:x1423637870543084:264:Complete:1357686943:0s(-11s) opc 700\n-1:0@lo:12345-0@lo:x1423637870543084:264:Complete:1357686943:0s(-11s) opc 700\n-1:0@lo:12345-0@lo:x1423637870543084:264:Complete:1357686943:0s(-11s) opc 700\n-1:0@lo:12345-0@lo:x1423637870543084:264:Complete:1357686943:0s(-11s) opc 700\n-1:0@lo:12345-0@lo:x1423637870543084:264:Complete:1357686943:0s(-11s) opc 700\n-1:0@lo:12345-0@lo:x1423637870543084:264:Complete:1357686943:0s(-11s) opc 700\n-1:0@lo:12345-0@lo:x1423637870543084:264:Complete:1357686943:0s(-11s) opc 700\n-1:0@lo:12345-0@lo:x1423637870543084:264:Complete:1357686943:0s(-11s) opc 700\n-1:0@lo:12345-0@lo:x1423637870543084:264:Complete:1357686943:0s(-11s) opc 700\n...\n^C",
